ContainerSettings.Title: Select Month
ContainerSettings.Description: Select a month to view its real estate sales details.

ContainerSettings.Title: Average Days on Market
ContainerSettings.Description: This number card shows the average number of days a property remains in inventory.

ContainerSettings.Title: Sales
ContainerSettings.Description: This number card shows the total income earned through property sales.

ContainerSettings.Title: Properties for Sale
ContainerSettings.Description: This KPI card shows the properties sold, total properties, and properties for sale.

ContainerSettings.Title: Card Title
ContainerSettings.Description: This number card shows the average number of calls and meetings made for a property sale.

ContainerSettings.Title: Avg. No. of Visits
ContainerSettings.Description: This number card shows the average number of times agents show a property to buyers.

ContainerSettings.Title: Rent
ContainerSettings.Description: This number card shows the total income earned through rent.

ContainerSettings.Title: Properties for Rent
ContainerSettings.Description: This KPI card shows the properties sold, total properties, and properties for rent.

ContainerSettings.Title: Sales vs Target
ContainerSettings.Description: This chart shows the difference between actual and target sales numbers for property sales.
ContainerSettings.SubTitle: Last 12 Months

ContainerSettings.Title: Sales by Region
ContainerSettings.Description: This map shows the sales of properties by region (in U.S. states).

ContainerSettings.Title: Property Inquiry Referrals
ContainerSettings.Description: This pie chart shows the number of properties referred by various referral categories like social media, marketplaces, digital ads, television ads, website, calls, and emails.

ContainerSettings.Title: Advertised vs. Sold
ContainerSettings.Description: This bar chart shows the number of properties advertised and sold by each agent of this company.

ContainerSettings.Title: Properties Sold and Rented by Agent
ContainerSettings.Description: This line chart shows the number of properties sold and rented by the real estate agents.

ContainerSettings.Title: Advertisement and Promotion Cost
ContainerSettings.Description: This is the amount of money a real estate company spent on advertising and promoting the properties.
ContainerSettings.SubTitle: Last 12 Months

ContainerSettings.Title: Recent Property Status
ContainerSettings.Description: This grid shows the recent property details: property name, agent, type, payment status, and price.

ContainerSettings.Title: Recent Inquiry Details
ContainerSettings.Description: This grid shows the most recent 25 inquiries for the properties.
